The paper deals with optimizing revenue in e-commerce operations, which involves handling large amounts of data and making personalized recommendations. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Electronic Commerce (cs.EC), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The use of vector space embeddings and the multinomial logit choice model also point towards cs.IR and cs.LG as likely sub-categories.
